      "message": "Good call.\nThese deletes are not needed (since it will inherit them from SkStream).\n\nWhen I removed the SkNoncopyable base class I put them in SkStream, then went on auto-pilot mode and just added them to all classes. But the deletes only need to be in the base.\n\n(The defaults should be in them all though.)\n\nAlthough, leaving them out may not make the \"this isn\u0027t copyable\" as obvious? Someone would need to hunt into the base to learn that.\n\n\n\nI\u0027m happy to either leave them or remove them, as you wish. They aren\u0027t required. They only provide readability, perhaps.",
